title: Janine A. Morris-Drama 99 FM
description: Janine A. Morris pens fiction that Booklist has called "reminiscent of Waiting to Exhale." In Drama 99 FM, Morris delivers a sizzling tale about three bodacious women who are living life to the fullest-and running the risk of crashing and burning. Naomi is a rising star in the music industry. Sereeta has a special talent for hooking up NBA ballers with luscious ladies. And Madison makes careers as the music director of the Big Apple's hottest radio station. Each is on top of the world, but affairs of the heart have a way of turning everything upside down
